            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4><i class="fa fa-paper-plane" aria-hidden="true"></i> Connect with people</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>It's blessing to know people that share the same interests as you. We are here to help!</p>
                <a href="/hobby" class="btn btn-default">See our hobbies list</a>
